{
  "message": "web: Fix navbar preload caching with session cache and staleTime config\n\n- Add client-side session cache (ensureSession) to prevent repeated\n  getSession calls on every preload - cache TTL 30s, cleared on logout\n- Configure defaultPreloadStaleTime: 30_000 on router for preload caching\n- Set explicit preloadStaleTime on home route to cache preloads while\n  keeping staleTime: 0 for fresh data on navigation\n- Update TanStack Router to 1.157.2\n\n\ud83d\udd2e View transcript: https://agentlogs.ai/s/kc1jcjqd5sqb78ab7r0df3y4",
